HEADWORD: Spirituelle
<hw>Spi`ri`tu`elle"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<def>Of the nature, or having the appearance, of a spirit; pure;
refined; ethereal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

